## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **insomnia chronic** = behavioral CBT-I 가 first-line, 약물 secondary. quantum-VQE 가 임상 efficacy 보장 X.
2. **DORA (suvorexant 2014 / lemborexant 2019 / daridorexant 2022) paradigm** — first non-GABA insomnia drug class; quantum-VQE 의 selectivity 향상 path.
3. **OSA 약물 부재** — CPAP 가 standard, solriamfetol/modafinil 은 EDS만 처리. 진정한 OSA-specific drug 의 큰 gap (TASK channel research).
4. **narcolepsy 1 type 1 (orexin deficiency) → orexin replacement therapy** = research. 단 small-molecule orexin receptor agonist 부재.
5. **RBD = PD prodrome** — 80%+ RBD develop PD/DLB within 10-15 years. quantum-VQE 의 neurodegen cross-link.
6. **circadian disorders** = light therapy + melatonin 가 standard, drug 한정. quantum-design 의 mechanism-specific.
7. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, sleep 임상 의미 한정.

